{
  "title": "Miniature Springy French Ciabatta Sandwich",
  "description": "A bain-marie cooked miniature ciabatta bread filled with a springy mix of tuna salad., A perfect brunch option that is easy on the palate.",
  "cuisine": "French",
  "diet": [
